column5: Who will be the fortunate ones to return to the BOQ this weekend ?
Mike - I hope to go down Saturday night and Sunday - I'll be on channel 72 if your around.   Don
i might go sunday,the weather is gonna be on our side,it might just be the last trip for me,i have to work on sat,so i will decide sat night,but i will get the boat ready just in case
No   I won't be there I have to finish the wiring in my new garage so I won't be fishing until the hard water arrives.I hope you do well this time out .Good Luck   .catch a 15 poudner  .Mike
Mike...."but Honey...the garage will still be here next week and the fishing opportunity won't" ! LOL Come on...you can do it..
I scored Monday off work, so I just might head down then....anyone going to be down there on Monday?
Mike we could always use my boat.
It wont be this weekend or next but the next is possability
I am heading down first thing in the morning for 3 days. Going to be doing some different tactics. Will report if it is successful.
We will need a 4X4.I won't put the gear away yet.
Thats o.k I happen to have one of those.
OK we have seen Petes report so when are you going to send some pics.
